        "subject": "LU-1431 osc: specify max_pages_per_rpc with units",
        "message": "LU-1431 osc: specify max_pages_per_rpc with units\n\nAllow specifying the osc.*.max_pages_per_rpc tunable with units\nsuffixes, so that it is possible to set it more easily, like:\n\n\tlctl set_param osc.*.max_pages_per_rpc=4M\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <andreas.dilger@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I4520219d4fedabdb4c018fad5384b8db42300c1e\n"
      },
